block main-content
  .about-container
    section.hero
      h1 About FurEverHome
      p We are dedicated to helping pets find their forever homes and supporting pet owners in their journey.

    section.our-mission
      .content
        h2 Our Mission
        p At FurEverHome, we believe every pet deserves a loving home. Our mission is to connect wonderful animals with caring families, promote responsible pet ownership, and support animal welfare initiatives in our community.
        p We strive to:
        ul
          li Create a world where no pet is left without a loving family
          li Educate the public about the joys and responsibilities of pet ownership
          li Provide support and resources to pet owners throughout their journey
          li Collaborate with shelters and rescues to increase adoption rates
          li Advocate for animal welfare and rights at local and national levels
      .image
        img(src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581888475780-27b6b0bc3690?w=500&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8M3x8cGV0JTIwY2FyZXxlbnwwfHwwfHx8MA%3D%3D" alt="Happy adopted pet")

    section.what-we-do
      h2 What We Do
      .services
        .service-card
          img(src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1601758124510-52d02ddb7cbd?w=500&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8M3x8cGV0JTIwYWRvcHRpb258ZW58MHx8MHx8fDA%3D" alt="Pet adoption")
          h3 Pet Adoption
          p We facilitate adoptions, matching pets with loving families.

        .service-card
          img(src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1588943211346-0908a1fb0b01?w=500&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8OHx8cGV0JTIwZWR1Y2F0aW9ufGVufDB8fDB8fHww" alt="Pet education")
