          p We work with local shelters and organize adoption events.

    section.our-story
      h2 Our Story
      p FurEverHome started as a small, local initiative in 2010. Founded by a group of passionate animal lovers, we've grown into a nationwide network of shelters, rescues, and pet care professionals. Our journey has been filled with wagging tails, purring companions, and countless heartwarming adoption stories.
      p Over the years, we've:
      ul
        li Facilitated over 100,000 pet adoptions across the country
        li Partnered with 500+ animal shelters and rescue organizations
        li Launched educational programs reaching millions of pet owners
        li Developed a comprehensive online platform for pet adoption and care resources
        li Initiated community outreach programs to assist low-income pet owners
      p Today, FurEverHome continues to grow and evolve, always keeping our core mission at heart: to create happy endings for pets and their human companions.

    section.get-involved
      h2 Get Involved
      .get-involved-content
        p There are many ways you can support our mission:
        ul
          li Adopt a pet
          li Volunteer at our shelters
          li Foster animals in need
          li Donate to support our work
        a.cta-button(href="/contact") Contact Us to Learn More